This is Ben Dragon's latest supplemental audio lecture to his book &quot;A MANUAL FOR HUMANITY&quot; Volume I, The Basics called &quot;The Widow's Son&quot;.

He gets into the more esoteric meaning of it. Hell. Here's a quote from his website.


&quot;In this essay, Ben Dragon goes into the hidden meanings of the term &quot;The Widow's Son&quot; where he will tell you of the occult, darker side of the term how it relates in the long term, to modern society and how it will affect and is affecting, you.&quot; 


Dat's a lot better than I could put it.

I found his stuff REALLY GOOD and I loved his book... something that I found tremendously insightful.

This guy not only sees through the system but PROVIDES SOLUTIONS and gives answers. Reading and listening to his stuff FORCED me to think. The answers that he gives helped me personally a lot. That's more than other researchers can say who just constantly say that the sky is falling and provide nothing to help us understand. I actually personally benefitted from reading what this guy has to say. So I thought that I would share it with others.



